description: Welcome to OverLoad Extreme Street Food. We are a family owned and operated food truck, striving to bring you great food and a good time. Our food truck is based on the most important things in life: food, fun, friends, and family. We strive to hear each and every one of our customers say "Wow, that was soooo good!"We offer burgers, subs, and more at a very reasonable price. Come visit us and be ready to have a great time. Be sure to check out our schedule for daily specials and our location. And don't forget, our domino tables are ready, so don't forget to bring your dominos.
name: OverLoad
